Class F2<A,B,C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fj.F2<A,B,C>

  • public abstract class F2<A,B,C>
extends java.lang.Object
    A transformation function of arity-2 from A and B to C. This type can be represented using the Java 7 closure syntax.
